description:
Download the free TonePrint here: http://www.tcelectronic.com/all-that-jazz

What pedal was used to make this TonePrint: http://www.tcelectronic.com/flashback-delay

Lee took a liking to our TonePrint pedals right of the bat - he loved how they keep tone intact. For this stereo ping-pong TonePrint, Lee cut a bit of the highs and the lows, to keep things tight yet unprovocative.
A nice ambient vibe with a bit of saturation for a nice warm edge and human voice.
